1. Checked Node.js version with: node -v
2. Opened the terminal in the project directory.
3. Attempted to install Sass version 3.7.4 using: npm install sass@3.7.4
   → Result: Version 3.7.4 does not exist in the npm registry.
4. Attempted to install node-sass@3.7.4
   → Result: Version 3.7.4 not found in the npm registry.
5. Installed the latest maintained Sass instead using: npm install sass
6. Verified installation with: npx sass --version
